|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| bridge legacy | field/class/helper/fallback | classification | owner liste | surface cible | delete/replace-consumer/keep-public-contract | scan/test | risque |

Allowed decisions:

- `delete`;
- `replace-consumer`;
- `keep-public-contract`;
- `needs-user-decision`.

